					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the policy value for Computer Configuration &gt;&gt; Windows Settings &gt;&gt; Security Settings &gt;&gt; Account Policies &gt;&gt; Password Policy &gt;&gt; "Enforce password history" to "24" passwords remembered.</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
