					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA></ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
				</STIG_DATA>
				<STIG_DATA>
					<VULN_ATTRIBUTE>Fix_Text</VULN_ATTRIBUTE>
					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the policy value for Computer Configuration &gt;&gt; Administrative Templates &gt;&gt; System &gt;&gt; Audit Process Creation &gt;&gt; "Include command line in process creation events" to "Enabled".</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
