					<ATTRIBUTE_DATA>Configure the policy value for Computer Configuration &gt;&gt; Administrative Templates &gt;&gt; Windows Components &gt;&gt; AutoPlay Policies &gt;&gt; "Turn off AutoPlay" to "Enabled:All Drives".</ATTRIBUTE_DATA>
